{"tid":866161,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟分享下你發過既夢","createTime":"2018-10-17T15:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T15:56:27.000Z","uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b40bbbf15a687d7f9316982f2521b6ebe78f75","tid":866161,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:41:01.000Z","msg":"記得好耐之前未同個ex一齊既時候<br />\n有一日夢見到佢 <br />\n我同佢搭緊地鐵<br />\n係地鐵到我錫左佢一啖<br />\n問題係現實世界中 我地係好耐無見好耐無聯絡了 當時完全唔知點解會夢到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後兩三個月後 我地無啦啦聯絡返 後尾都一齊左 然後沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人會好奇點解成日發埋啲咁奇怪既夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底夢係咪另一個平行世界既我？"},{"pid":"83e28a030152e0067458fc1c3c0f6d00d73aaf3e","tid":866161,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:43:20.000Z","msg":"識到細粒靚女女朋友 係地鐵壁咚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4376e6527178faed09fed99e67ea56ad5fef613","tid":866161,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83e28a030152e0067458fc1c3c0f6d00d73aaf3e","tid":866161,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:43:20.000Z","msg":"識到細粒靚女女朋友 係地鐵壁咚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:55:06.000Z","msg":"認真咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5646f4f92f64be12641bbaed340021ae2b0eff5","tid":866161,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e4376e6527178faed09fed99e67ea56ad5fef613","tid":866161,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83e28a030152e0067458fc1c3c0f6d00d73aaf3e","tid":866161,"uid"